  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Bouganville Rooms (Ground Floor) </strong>are about 25m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single bed). They have a ground floor terrace and a bath with showerhead. Rooms with a shower are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>Oleandro Rooms</strong> are around 25m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single bed). They have a balcony with garden views and a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Bouganville Rooms for sole use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p>Interconnecting rooms are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A tourist tax of €2.50 per person per night is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
